@node not09 "PAUL BURKEY AND EPIC MARKETING ANNOUNCE COOPERATION"

              PAUL BURKEY AND EPIC MARKETING ANNOUNCE COOPERATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Paul Burkey and Epic Marketing proudly announce a long term cooperation. The
goal of this new cooperation is to bring great strategy games to the Amiga
community. The first fruits of this cooperation will bring "Foundation's
Director's Cut" to the community. This is Foundation brought up-to-date with all
available and one forthcoming update. It will be priced at £ 14.99 (DM 49.- or
25 Euro) and is mainly aimed at those Amiga users that never bought the original
game. "Foundation's Director's Cut" will be released in about 2 weeks time and
will be available direct from Epic Marketing Germany (Tel: +49/(0)7071 400492,
E-Mail: info@epic-marketing.de) or Epic Marketing UK (Tel: +44/(0)1793 432176
E-Mail: islona@dialin.net). Preorders are welcome and can already be placed with
Epic.

Foundation is a real-time strategy war game which incorporates familiar strategy
elements with interesting new concepts. Accomplished strategy game players will
